narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, it is another of Marta's classes. If she likes you, you will learn and get a good grade. If she doesn't, you will still learn but struggle a little bit more.
If you want to improve your Portuguese and be able to read book well and improve vocabulary, definitely take it!
I would definitely urge anyone who has taken L3 to continue with Portuguese and take L4! It's not a lot of work in class, and you get to practice speaking a lot more.
